        "KirikiriEmscriptenInterface",
        "DOM",
        "KeyboardEvent"
      ],
      "testScript": "plugins/tests/menu_smoke.tjs",
      "status": "planned",
      "implementation": "不移植 Win32 HMENU/HWND；实现 MenuItem、Window.menu、caption、enabled、checked、shortcut、onClick 等脚本可见行为，底层用 DOM 或 Canvas 菜单和键盘事件分发。"
    },
    {
