      "implementationType": "side-module",
      "compatLevel": "A",
      "priority": "P0",
      "phase": 1,
      "reason": "KAG 扩展解析基础插件；用于验证 Emscripten side module 插件链路。",
      "exports": [
        "V2Link",
        "V2Unlink"
      ],
      "dependencies": [],
      "testScript": "plugins/tests/KAGParser_smoke.tjs",
      "status": "blocked",
      "implementation": "源码已拉取（plugins/third_party/KAGParser）。已修 3 处 krkrz 版本漂移：TJS_NCM_REG_THIS 改 classobj、删除 TVPInternalError 旧式定义、覆盖 TJS_NATIVE_SET_ClassID。剩余阻塞：krkrsdl2 移除了插件 stub 机制（FuncStubs.h 仅 1 行，主引擎不调 TVPInitImportStub），side-module 无法调用 TVPGetScriptDispatch 等主 wasm 函数。需先重建 side-module stub 机制（运行 makestub.py 生成完整 FuncStubs）才能继续。详见 plugin-compatibility-execution-steps.md §7.7。"
    },
